<subSubSection id="15DE5FE0FF8CEF4FFF42F95FFDFBF8C8" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFF8CEF4FFF42F95FFC7FF8F4" blockId="36.[151,1437,1697,1905]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF8CEF4FFF42F95FFEE7F8BC" bold="true" box="[199,338,1770,1796]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Comments:</emphasis>
This is the first record of this species for the 
<collectingRegion id="9F00C289FF8CEF4FFCE0F95FFC44F8BD" box="[869,1009,1770,1797]" country="Brazil" name="Parana" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Paraná state</collectingRegion>
. Individuals are green and have been found on leaves of forest shrubs. This species seems to be less abundant than the other 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF8CEF4FFBE9F8BBFAEEF890" box="[1132,1371,1806,1832]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF8CEF4FFBE9F8BBFAB6F890" box="[1132,1283,1806,1832]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Grammadera</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
mentioned above, since we were able to collect only few individuals of them.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFF8CEF4FFF42F8E3FDFBF8C8" blockId="36.[151,1437,1697,1905]" box="[199,590,1878,1905]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
